Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去跟穹講的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你一起講不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛  反應真誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？啊啊  我馬上去做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  食材已經用完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘買了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  明天我做咖哩飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹你喜歡的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會能跟你談談嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.48,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（在哪？）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.48,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（…學校）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是沒談成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  二位  一大早就那麼火熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  難道是昨天在游泳池邊確定情侶關係了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  說中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  你得請客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我分享一點幸福又不會遭報應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降投降投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點停手  亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到晚上五點了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟那傢伙是青梅竹馬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒那傢伙總是一個人發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有氣無力  漠不關心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從你來到這兒之後  奈緒變了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她開始會笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想  你還真是特別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  一副那麼複雜的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的奈緒  開朗  樂於助人  應該總是笑著才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小穹也叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來湊什麼熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我跟悠說好這頓午飯由他請我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以嘛  悠的東西就是我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我明白了  那就大家一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得人家還特意邀請你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒說過非要人家請我不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種客套我最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的事情…還沒跟穹說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.45,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我先回去了。）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.45,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（會晚點。）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…總覺得時機對不上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我今天肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  不用那麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個痕跡是中獎的證明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要是挑到了這個  就隨你吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹能吃咖哩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做咖哩飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？  自小學夏令營以來我就沒做過咖哩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還沒回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很討女孩子喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你也稍微謙虛點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和小悠一起吐西瓜子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒還錯把西瓜子吞下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就沒再見小悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把它填滿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的日子  我們填滿它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出一副姐姐的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恬不知恥地插到我和悠之間來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個夏天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想把悠搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我還不懂你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻隱隱約約知道這是些見不得人的勾當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再靠近我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再出現在悠的面前了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是悠的咖哩更好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的奈緒  開朗  樂於助人  應該總是笑著才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒她  從某一個夏天開始  性格有了很大的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那個夏天開始  就一直獨自痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子  這樣子只會倒退回過去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  從昨天開始好像身體有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝關心  我會轉告她的  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒  身體如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛春日野君打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  放學之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了  要準備上下一節課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共1876元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再來玩吐西瓜子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像過去一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易和奈緒言歸於好  這樣子只會倒退回過去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好地向穹道歉祈求她的諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓她認同我們的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認識的奈緒  就應該常帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過奈緒還是笑著比較可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小悠  小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了很多  樣子可能不太好看  味道可是一流的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮玉米好了  要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我也不想後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到穹肯原諒我們之前  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說我和奈緒之間的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真純情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太見外了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:18:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘴巴就是大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮哥雖然是跟我們說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說沒有提到兩人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但聽他一說  馬上就能猜到是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了成就兩位的關係的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我藏不住話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  大家今天就盡情享受  為兩位打好關係做支援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要獲得小穹的認同  大家就放心把這個任務交給我亮平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠這樣當然最好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮哥認真過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  說起來小穹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邀請過她了可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好的小穹泳裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:42.09,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}待續
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.94,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}胸口COME ON
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和悠一起去海邊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍藍的海  白白的沙灘  正是兩人的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…本應如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人數是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我身為女僕身懷各種秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無畏無懼地驅逐敵人  創造和悠兩人世界的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我上個洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子真讓人心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我也要上洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.48,0:23:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開  小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的吧  是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  絕對不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為懲罰  要對我言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現新的玩法了
